WEBVTT

00:06:58.604 --> 00:07:01.134
Na unaweza, pia. Sio ngumu.

00:07:01.739 --> 00:07:05.643
Kabla hatujajaza toroli zetu za manunuzi
na jalala zetu

00:07:05.667 --> 00:07:08.298
na bidhaa ambazo hatuna uhitaji nazo,

00:07:08.322 --> 00:07:11.938
tusite kwanza tukiwa tunafanya
manunuzi mtandaoni

00:07:11.962 --> 00:07:17.646
na kuwaza mara mbili kuhusu kile
ambacho kweli tunakitaka:

00:07:17.670 --> 00:07:20.315
dunia maridhawa tunayoweza kuita nyumbani.

00:07:20.394 --> 00:07:21.556
Asante.

00:07:21.580 --> 00:07:24.846
(Makofi na shangwe)